## tool-session-model-reset: session, model, and reset tool definitions

### session(action: str, session_id: str = "") → str
Manage agent sessions.
- action="list"   — list all active sessions with their IDs, model, and history size. Requires read gate approval.
- action="delete" — delete a session by ID (shorthand integer or full session ID). Requires write gate approval.

### model(action: str, model_key: str = "") → str
Manage the active LLM model for this session.
- action="list" — show all available models (current model marked). Always allowed.
- action="set"  — switch to the named model (model_key required). Requires write gate approval.

### reset() → str
Clear conversation history for the current session.
Requires write gate approval (controlled by !reset_gate_write, default: gated).
